				<td colspan="2"><span>I picked tunare half-elf. If I could re-roll I'd have made an agnostic cat. 
<br />
I didn't know what to put points into when I first started so I put them into str, sta and cha. If I could change that I would have put them all in sta and cha. 
<br />
Your melee damage is not what's important, it can be a good contribution but when picking equipment, keep in mind the fact that our songs are what define us, don't waste money on fancy weapons unless you have plenty to blow. 
<br />
Try to save up for a Troubador's mace or a Gem inlaid longsword, other good bard weps are Sionche's Partisan, D'zok Wristsnapper, and symphonic saber.
<br />
