				<td colspan="2"><span>I get sick of seeing Half Elf Bards, before Luclin models you were wading through them because they looked good in plate compared to other classes. Now it's Vah Shir bards that are absolutely everywhere on my server.
<br />

<br />
<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">Wood Elf Bard - More into how they look than actually doing their job</span></blockquote>
